      <title>道明旗下美国零售银行一度备受推崇，但现在却拖累其股价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/td-s-us-retail-bank-once-prized-now-drags-down-its-stock-price</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多道明银行斥巨资进军美国市场本应能促进其增长。然而，这反而拖累了盈利能力，并严重损害了该行的声誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/td-s-us-retail-bank-once-prized-now-drags-down-its-stock-price</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:32:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
