      <title>福特斥资 19 亿美元进军 SUV 业务，进一步退出电动汽车领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/ford-pulls-back-further-from-evs-with-1-9-billion-suv-pivot</link>
